info.author: IOAM
info.description: `NumberGen` provides a parameterized family of objects producing reproducible streams of numeric values, such as pseudorandom numbers.  `NumberGen` is supplied with the `Param <https://pypi.python.org/pypi/param/>`_ package, which it complements.
info.name: numbergen
info.summary: Number sequences, currently included with the Param package
